
                            About application
                            ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

1. General information
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
  This software is a power supply sizing application.
  There are these calculations:
  - Buffered Graetz-bridge rectifier
  - Buffered full wave rectifier
  - Buffered half wave rectifier
  - Capacitive divider for serial heater circuit (AC 50Hz)
  - Current regulator with LM117/LM317/LM237/LM337 integrated circuit
  - Full wave rectifier
  - Graetz-bridge rectifier
  - Half wave rectifier
  - Voltage regulator with LM117/LM317/LM237/LM337 integrated circuit
  - Voltage regulator with Zener-diode
  - Voltage regulator with gas filled voltage stabiliser tube
 
  This is a software, which does not cost money (maybe you must pay for use
Internet).  The lope conditions is the acceptance and observance of the European
Union Public Licence.
   
   OS support: FreeBSD, Linux and Windows.
   Language support: English and Hungarian.

2. Installer packages
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
a. for FreeBSD
   powersupplies-0.4.1-FreeBSD-Port.shar   port package
   powersupplies-0.4.1.txz                 binary package

b. for Linux
   powersupplies-0.4.1-1.i586.rpm          binary package
   powersupplies-0.4.1-i586-1.txz          binary package
   powersupplies-0.4.1-i586.bin            installer programme
   powersupplies-0.4.1-i586.tar.gz         binary package
   powersupplies-0.4.1.x86.package         binary package
   powersupplies_0.4.1-1_i386.deb          binary package

c. for Windows
   powersupplies-0.4.1-win32.exe           installer application
   powersupplies-0.4.1-win32.msi           binary package
   powersupplies-0.4.1-win32.zip           binary package

d. source code
   powersupplies-0.4.1.tar.gz              source package

3. Settings
~~~~~~~~~~~
  On Linux and FreeBSD use 'LANG' environment variable to set language of the
application. (English: en_US, Hungarian: hu_HU)

